rcm / repeatcomment           Repeats the current mission's most recent comment

   Format:
      ;rcm                    Repeats the most recent comment

   Notes:
      Repeats the comment most recently displayed by the current mission, in
         case it has scrolled out of view.
      See the help for ';startmission' for more information about missions.

   User commands:
      rcm / repcm / repeatcm / repeatcomment
